<h1>The 4th Dublin Core Metadata Workshop Report</h1>
<h3>DC-4<BR>
March 3 - 5, 1997<BR>
National Library of Australia, Canberra </h3>
</center>
<p>
<center>
Stuart Weibel, OCLC, <I>weibel@oclc.org</I><BR>
