<h4> Workshop Steering Committee: </h4>
<p>
The essence of this series of workshops is the building of a
multidisciplinary consensus on the nature of network resource
discovery. Whatever success is achieved in this process is due to the
commitment and collective wisdom of the participants. The support of
the following individuals as workshop steering committee members is
exemplary of this contribution.</p>

